{
  "stem": "21978.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at that moment, I had the-- the reason to approach him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, he was a person that you could really think that he's nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you wouldn't have met him there, if you wouldn't have known what is he doing, you would have even thought that he's a nice man-- when he was whistling.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew that he had a wife and a child in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the child was sick-- we were-- on the grapevine, we were told.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I know that we have wished the child should die, that he would know what sorrow is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The child didn't die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't witness his behavior in any other way than just examining other twins, sitting there, measuring, writing, talking to the-- through the interpreter, Polish interpreter, telling them something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He even gave my sister and me white bread and some cheese.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was after we had the transfusion, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I haven't seen him doing anything to anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I only know what the witnesses told us at the trial of Mengele in his absence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In '85, Mengele was tried by the Nuremberg judges-- prosecutors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The trial-- trial was in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Jana Wendt, from took Annetta and myself as survivors-- twins-- from Australia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were the only ones they could find here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were other twins who were survivors from all over Europe, all over the world-- Israel, America, and some-- some came from Europe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not only twins, but they were also dwarfs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were also doctors who were in charge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were giving testimony about Mengele's students.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I have heard about trial-- about the experiment that he has made on others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "For instance, toddlers, twins, that he had then sewn together like Siamese things.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
